<h3>To <i>subscribe</i> to the NetRexx mailing list</h3>
<ul><li>
Just send a piece of e-mail to <a href="mailto:ibm-netrexx-subscribe@hursley.ibm.com">
majordomo@hursley.ibm.com</a> with the text:
<pre>
  subscribe
  end
</pre>
in the body of the mail.
</ul>

<h3>To <i>unsubscribe</i> from the NetRexx mailing list</h3>
<ul><li>
To remove your subscription, just send a piece of e-mail to
<a href="mailto:ibm-netrexx-unsubscribe@hursley.ibm.com">
majordomo@hursley.ibm.com</a> with the text:
<pre>
  unsubscribe
  end
</pre>
in the body of the mail.
</ul>

<h3>To <i>'post'</i> (send mail) to everyone on the NetRexx mailing list</h3>
<ul><li>
Send your e-mail to <a href="mailto:ibm-netrexx@hursley.ibm.com">
ibm-netrexx@hursley.ibm.com</a>.
<p>
Please keep your posts short and to-the-point &#150; you'll get better
replies, that way!
</ul>

<h3>The mailing list archives</h3>
<ul><li>... can be found at
<a href="http://ibm-netrexx.215625.n3.nabble.com">http://ibm-netrexx.215625.n3.nabble.com</a>
<p>
<font size=-1>
Note: some recent archives may not be listed on the index page; these
can be accessed using the same URL as ones which are listed, updating
the year and month appropriately.</font>
</ul>

<h3>Problems with the mailing list?</h3>
<ul><li>
Please send mail to the Hursley webmaster at
<a href="http://www.hursley.ibm.com/~www/">www@hursley.ibm.com</a>
describing the problem in detail.
<p>
Don't send mail about problems to the list .. or you'll likely just make
the problem worse!
</ul>
